ZONE 7 — FORWARD DECLARATIONS OF TYPES USED IN THIS HEADER
════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

Purpose:
  Break include cycles. Declare types that this header mentions in parameter
  or return types but whose full definition is not needed here.

Template:
